[dengan melayan orang di sini?]

714
00:40:09,180 --> 00:40:10,750
[Balik dengan saya.]

715
00:40:10,750 --> 00:40:11,910
[Ayah memerlukan awak.]

716
00:40:11,910 --> 00:40:12,980
[Awak cuma memerlukan kerja]

717
00:40:12,980 --> 00:40:13,550
[dan atur cara awak.]

718
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:15,030
[Bilakah awak memerhatikan saya?]

719
00:40:15,690 --> 00:40:17,060
Rupa-rupanya, dialah Rui Rui.

720
00:40:17,660 --> 00:40:19,110
Dia dah lama berkenalan dengan Si Yan.

721
00:40:20,630 --> 00:40:22,630
Namun, kenapa Si Yan berpura-pura tidak mengenali dia?

722
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:49,460
[Cik, percayai saya.]

723
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,840
[Memang bukan saya yang buat begitu.]

724
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:52,840
[Pengintip!]

725
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,730
[Untunglah awak untuk dilucutkan jawatan saja.]

726
00:40:54,730 --> 00:40:55,410
[Jangan, cik.]

727
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:56,090
[Ke tepi!]

728
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,350
[Jangan biar saya jumpa awak lagi!]


